                                課程簡介
                            

                                 
                            

                                 
                            

                                Introduction
                            





                                本課程共分成兩個單元第壹單元：｢建築工程｣第貳單元：｢建築防災計畫｣上述兩單元，均以實務說明及案例分析為講授主軸。各單元之課程大綱如下所示：壹、建築工程    施工與管理，內容包括 1. 營建產業之特質 2. 重要施工作業簡介    a. 基礎工程    b. 連續壁工程    c. 地下結構施工法    d. RC結構工程    e. 鋼骨工程    f. 帷幕牆工程    g. 室內裝修工程 3. 營建管理的基本目標與管理需求    a. 工程進度    b. 工程品質    c. 工程安全    d. 工程成本 4. 實例操作貳、建築防災概要 1. 燃燒概述     a. 燃燒機制     b. 燃燒型態     c. 燃燒行為 2. 建築火災行為     a. 居室火災行為     b. 建築物火災行為     c. 建築火災延燒行為 3. 一般建築物防災計畫     a. 防止火災發生     b. 防止初期火災擴大     c. 防止火災延燒擴大     d. 防災管理 4. 特殊建築物防災計畫     a. 演藝廳、劇場     b. 地下空間（地下街）     c. 集合住宅     d. 體育館、展覽館     e. 大型複合空間     f. 大型商場 5. 防災計畫書     a. 一般建築物     b. 地下建築物 6. 避難計畫

《 課程簡介 -- English 》
                                This whole course is divided into two groups.The first group is Construction and management,and the second group is building fire safety planning. The main ideas of two courses are focused inpracticality events and cases studies.The outline of each course as showed in below:First Construction and management.Course content including: 1. Industry characteristic of Construction  2. Brief introduction of important construction Engineering     a. Foundation structure Engineering     b. Continuous wall structure Engineering     c. Construction method of Underground structure     d. RC structural Engineering     e. Steel structure Engineering     f. Curtain wall structure Engineering     g. Interior decoration Engineering  3. The basic goal of Construction management and demand of management     a. Project progress     b. Project quality     c. project is safety     d. project cost 4. Cases StudyBuilding fire safety planning 1. Burning concept     a. Burning mechanism     b. Burning type     c. Burning behavior 2. Burning behavior of building     a. Fire behavior of room     b. Fire behavior of building     c. Spreading behavior of building fire 3. Fire safety planning of regular building     a. Prevent fire occurring     b. Prevent initial fire expanding     c. Prevent fire spreading     d. Fire safety management 4. Fire safety planning of special building     a. Showing room, theater     b. Underground space ( Underground street)     c. Compound building     d. Gymnasium, Exhibition hall     e. Large-scale compound space     f. Shopping mall 5. Contents of fire safety planning     a. regular building     b. Underground building 6. Escape planning











